'''Masterblades''' were [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] [[Bladeborn]] who were weapon masters that won ten or more [[Lightsaber duel/Legends|duels]] against [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]]-wielding opponents. The title was one of great pride for it signified the user's skill in defeating the weapon of the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]], or other Sith. As a sign of their [[Military rank/Legends|rank]], these masterblades were given a [[Sith Tremor Sword]] which they used lethally against their enemies.

